[Fri, 08 Nov 2024 05:27:59 GMT] "There's a guy out there who thinks the universe is just a bunch of triangles and now every time I see a triangle I feel like I'm being watched.\n\n\nHe's got this whole theory about how everything can be reduced to simple shapes and it's honestly kind of terrifying.\n\n\nPeople are starting to believe him too, I see it in the way they obsess over fractals and sacred geometry.\n\n\nI don't know if he's right but I do know that every time I see a triangle now I feel a shiver run down my spine."
